<h1 id="al-folio">al-folio</h1>
<div data-align="center">
<p><a href="https://alshedivat.github.io/al-folio/"><img
src="readme_preview/al-folio-preview.png" alt="Preview" /></a></p>
<p><strong>A simple, clean, and responsive <a
href="https://jekyllrb.com/">Jekyll</a> theme for
academics.</strong></p>
